NAME
    String::SimpleEscape - Simple string escaping & unescaping

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of String::SimpleEscape (from Perl
    distribution String-SimpleEscape), released on 2020-05-28.

DESCRIPTION
    A very simple backslash escaping/unescaping utility, with only four
    escapes known: "\n" (for \012), "\t" (for tab), "\\" (for backslash),
    "\"" (for doublequotes).

FUNCTIONS
  simple_escape_string
  simple_unescape_string
HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/String-SimpleEscape>.

